{
  "stem": "7273.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And four-- that was four years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we made an examination for-- I went to the Deutsche [INAUDIBLE] Gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that-- that was then the continuation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I finished my gymnasium in-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I don't know now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What it would have been?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In '37, I think. '37, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went for a year to a-- a finishing school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything what is necessary to be a fantastic housewife.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I learned cooking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I learned sewing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I learned shopping, because even that you got to know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And even-- even cleaning and all what you need to-- to have a nice home and to be good in your house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in Myslowice, where my grandparents lived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by train, it was not so long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was 20 minutes by train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So only Friday night, I didn't go home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stayed till Sunday by my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I-- from small on, I said, the first travel I remember was maybe I was five years of age with my mom and grandma to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from then on, we-- when I went to school, we had always holidays.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went to-- mostly to Germany to a seaside resort, because we lived close to mountains, but not to the sea.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So for, say, six weeks in my holidays, we went to mostly Kolobrzeg, which is on the Baltic Sea.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when there was a bit of time left, we went for two weeks to the mountains to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think they must have been the Beskydy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, different sports.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I played tennis, and I swan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I learned swimming in Kolobrzeg as a very young kid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, well, when we got a bit older, we learned dancing, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
